Source: libmongoc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: A. Jesse Jiryu Davis <jesse@mongodb.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-autoreconf, yelp-tools, yelp-xsl, libbson-dev, pkg-config, libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Section: libs
Homepage: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver/tree/debian

Package: libmongoc-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libmongoc-1.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - dev files
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains all files necessary to develop applications which
 use libmongoc.

Package: libmongoc-1.0-0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - runtime files
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains the libmongoc runtime libraries, for applications that
 have been built with libmongoc.

Package: libmongoc-dbg
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Depends: libmongoc-1.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - debug symbols
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains the debugging symbols for libmongoc's public and
 private runtime libraries.

Package: libmongoc-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - documentation
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains the man pages for libmongoc.

Package: libmongoc-priv0
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - private runtime
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains a private runtime library, for projects like the
 MongoDB driver for PHP that access internals of libmongoc. This private
 library is unstable and undocumented, not suitable for public use.
 Future versions will have unannounced breaking ABI and API changes.

Package: libmongoc-priv-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libmongoc-priv (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB C client library - private headers
 libmongoc is the officially supported MongoDB client library for C
 applications.
 .
 This package contains private headers for projects like the MongoDB
 driver for PHP that access internals of libmongoc. These private headers
 are unstable and undocumented, not suitable for public use. Future
 versions of these headers will have unannounced breaking ABI and API
 changes.
